[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering FieldSerializer Tests**\n\nI need to create a test using the public API for the FieldSerializer focused on a class with an int field. I’m pondering whether to instantiate ObjectIntField when ASM access isn't available. It seems like ObjectField subclasses are used for primitive fields. There’s an existing FieldSerializer test for IntArray, but I'm unsure if the int size coverage is active due to remaining lines — possibly related to accessIndex and ASM. I need to understand how FieldSerializer makes its choices.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0bed2e00e7b5b3690169f280a285088196bc85339923154154\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8oClUmy_AYL_tsLW2ujT3fjjky9bFIFd8cn3ApOQ2jc1Dl46kWQEoCmYUCLhoSAGK1VSWM56TW2I7rLtpQI3ry0xxrWQscaG8iymEjjkLOtDhC2zu1okaNKQOuuP1wk2d17MsX3eRXCGFLmD3a7KSnjDNerCbvtG0HxlCLtwLheNDmjOIEI1Si7ekunhidw8KKb1oWrePBwKnWbyHFngTu4-sQc_S9I3ryGH-wF84z0vvD6YQF54fG8TPPTFXFjwUQSKC-Oxces6L5OhMGFbnoSJwzXUlF_WIdWy-spkGIc8tYYnjXgUCtEZSENyayhDZnIuT6c-KzMl_B_9fG3q76ugJbf92N9QdkuUCQ_N4VZ0jjFi3dFJ3j64wlJM-ujnohFm0lUoLABGA2dKlu_ue1DxOBQD-z9UX5Q1gfBovepmSK5HkCFjxamVfP-kIUIZBWt0xZ25afj6Vkxrw-VlL3IEPVD-dbiyK62bQ13pQljOEEDqXxZHpfHWteFJ12zNp0t9_YvEnuaJ9rxSmgy4DRXtonaJqCnBAJU-SQSzWgTdzPkjlx-Mw8Mc_u5O9Pd5fU4_q6mTi2jakoLerJhUlRMd2sF0dODjADSmrDI82Z1LPGLtjA-tGaeDVZAhGTcmu5zADxHT2eIRQ9pIspzMlCxQmYOv95cbvpmj0RONWiFWt-EfPa6Tl64ixEXp46TCkYHnK9mfHF2eh3Xr853-sQQtoXKuhStD5NJRlFhx-VDHDlpg8fJks5mVigbAR4IyjlzLdKVhGpY6Yz0GGgtc0DyIfSmQ6WzuC_X5N3EAvj-AuMansDPFnL66PYSsmSfF1tOwavV2t88IWM20QkXmdZwo9AsKGz4folaG1_8JhxqcmwJs-y95_4AvKFFkw4-sfix2dpcI10aJ6RrRPzjUDEn9qTRZCd7LrICszGbPH1ZBb1BKH-7y0EPqg8NagiO3rP8LvP8_vcaneuOdHifi1vfx9ss40hwNyFNNCiLNuh0glV0SD9pnXL6utMaDtGEwrBuDukDRrMqseaoO1rn4rBtX1bMs1s7G6KkHiD_KCRuTrcXRqkOvkyUDRJeqQiVY2Y2OWYV0TZoP5ZhzyblfpHBV0-lQKs_NGKtZGLnQNOwglDAqxlz77PfIeh2fKigz1A3vUE8UdGc3oQOs3wspdgCloFkmdJSXCyLi-yTIaazdJ2c3iK_5E6h9vD85blm8